===Intransitive Verb===
====Etymology====
OE. alihten, fr. AS. a&#772; li&#772; htan; prefix a&#772;- (compare with. Goth. us-, G. er-, orig. meaning out) + li&#772; htan, to alight, orig. to render light, to remove a burden from, fr. li&#772; ht, leoht, light.  See  [[Light]], v.i.

====Definitions====
